into R for analysis in R and that works great for things that might be a few gigabytes or

00:01:22.059 --> 00:01:29.419
even tens of gigabytes but there's also, and that's fine because a lot of problems

00:01:29.419 --> 00:01:36.379
don't require any more firepower than that and for that set of problems, R will take

00:01:36.379 --> 00:01:41.660
care of the solution by and large through, you know, the large number of packages that

00:01:41.660 --> 00:01:43.379
are available to us.

